Astronaut Jessica Watkins, ’10, talks with
STANFORD
magazine
NASA flight engineer Jessica Watkins, ’10, spoke with
STANFORD
magazine from aboard the ISS Expedition 67 about finding her path at Stanford Earth (now part of the Stanford Doerr School of Sustainability) and what it’s like to sleep in space.
